Yomenya Goemon 洋麵屋五右衛門

tip.text: Good food, good ambience, excellent service
Must tries : Braised pork knuckles (that melts off the bones), fish head curry, chap chye, ngoh hiong (super crispy) w a whole lot of belachan. Service is EXCELLENT as well. 72++ for 4pax #Peranakan
Soup kettle :. Crumbly bits of broccoli in my broccoli soup, not my thing
For girls : order the wimpy burger instead. The fat basterd sounds a whole lot more tempting but it's also mad filling.
Beer-battered onion rings are pretty good, really big too. A tad oily for our liking though.
The Berkshire Korrubutu Pork Neck = 4.5 stars. ORDER THEIR FOIE GRAS, no regrets. Chocolate souffle's also better than their hot souffle!
